  <div class="flex w-full h-full">
    <div class="flex flex-col justify-between md:max-h-[300px] gap-4">
      <div class="flex flex-col h-full">
        <p class="m-0 font-light text-xl">
          Hi, I'm <b class="font-bold">Laurynas Gailius</b>, a beginner software
          engineer looking to find his way in the world of programming.
          Currently studying at <a
            href="https://www.vu.lt/en/"
